## List.rbegin() method

Returns a reverse iterator pointing to the last element in the list (i.e., its reverse beginning).

**Signature:**

```typescript
rbegin(): ListIterator<T>;
```
**Returns:**

[ListIterator](doc/markdown/./base.listiterator.md)<!-- -->&lt;T&gt;
